<h2 id="free-online-tools-for-climate-data-visualizationmanipulation">Free online tools for climate data visualization/manipulation</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.giss.nasa.gov/tools/panoply/">Panoply by NASA</a>: data viewer (on maps) of 
netCDF, HDF and GRIB files; I use it on Windows/macOS.</li>
  <li><a href="http://nco.sourceforge.net/">NCO toolkit</a>: command-line program to manipulate netCDF files; 
I often use that on Linux.</li>
</ul>
